# UI / 90s Hacker Theme

- Palette: background `#0a0a0a`, text `#00ff41`, accent `#00ffff`, warning `#ffb000`
- Monospace font: Courier New, DejaVu Sans Mono
- Square borders (no border-radius) — CRT aesthetic
- Labels with `>>` terminal prefix
- Logs with timestamp `[HH:mm:ss]`
- Button text in UPPERCASE (BOOT ZAP, RUN RECON)
- Tabs: `[ ZAP ]` and `[ RECON ]`
- **All UI strings in English**

Do not add widgets without connecting to an existing service.
